description:
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join our Portering team at our Basingstoke site as a Bank Porter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Bank Porter in Hampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust you will play an important part in the provision of excellent care to our patients, and be part of a friendly and dedicated team. Porters play a crucial part in keeping the hospital working by moving patients, goods and equipment between wards and departments to where they are needed in addition to controlling and removing the clinical waste to keep out Hospital clean and hygienic.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Bank is an ideal way of earning extra money or starting a career in the Trust. It offers work on an ad hoc or flexible basis as you will be covering shortages in staffing levels of our permanent staff, but ideally you will be available to work full time time hours across a variety of shifts 24/7 7 days a week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;The successful applicant must hold the following:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flexible in their approach to work in order to meet the needs of a busy hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Willingness to work on a rolling or ad-hoc shift pattern to cover early, late, nights and weekend shifts&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience in a hospital based environment is preferred but not essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The successful applicant must be able to demonstrate the following:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A motivated “can do” attitude&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Organised and structured in your approach to work&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to deal with challenges in a positive manner&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to maintain the confidentiality required when working in a patient environment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If all of the above sounds appealing and you want to help us further shape our commitment of maintaining clinical excellence in a positive and professional environment then please submit your application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;A standard disclosure from the Disclosure and Barring Service will be applied for in the event of a successful application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further details or to arrange an informal discussion or visit please email: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;tim.nicholls@hhft.nhs,uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
